 Other fan ke mukabale fast speed nahi hai. Lekin fan me cool hawa aati hai. Ye thoda thik features hai. Usha ke fan me sounds bahut kam hai. Jise aapko aaram ki need aa sakti hai. Abhi tak 1week se use kar raha hoon me fan mujhe aur koi dikkat nahi aai hai. Warranty mujhe 2year ki diya hai. Ye bahut achhi baat hai. Jin bhaiyo ko jayda fast speed chahiye ye unko purchase nahi karna chahiye. Lekin Jin bhaiyo ko raat ko sone ke time cool hawa vo bhi bina sounds ke unke liye ek achha option hai. Vo log ise purchase kar sakte hai.
